          **cohort index**

          cohort index

          [106]:
          def create_cohort_index(first_month, first_year, latest_month,latest_year):
          year_diff = latest_year - first_year
          month_diff = latest_month - first_month
          index = year_diff*12 + month_diff + 1
          return index
